g.text: What is the total number of new hospitalizations and current hospitalizations as of May 19, 2020?
As of May 19, 2020, there were 100 new hospitalizations and 2,606 current hospitalizations. The information
about new hospitalizations is found on page 20 with the text "100 new hospitalizations as of 5/19 (1.6%
increase)" (<box>(0.04, 0.38, 0.24, 0.43)</box>, page 20). The information about current hospitalizations can be
